Name: Wicked Tuna
Title: Wreck It Ralph
Desc: An old acquaintance is back in Gloucester, Mass., to fight for the title as the best fisherman.
LongDescription: An old acquaintance is back in Gloucester, Mass., to fight for the title as the best fisherman, but the fleet makes him feel unwelcome; for one fisherman, the sea is not big enough for both of them.
